data.description: Tastefully updated 2 bedroom, 2 bath single level home. Updated flooring throughout, fireplace in the living room, large dining area and open concept wrap around kitchen. Office area could be used as another bedroom, plus large family room that was used as a master bedroom. Vinyl fence around big back yard with covered patio, sprinkler system, two storage sheds and what could be a nice water feature with some TLC. Single attached garage and what was used as RV parking to the right of the driveway.
